## 10.2 RSNA Pneumonia Detection Challenge

### Task

Pneumonia opacity detection on chest X-ray using bounding boxes.

### Metric

- mean Average Precision across IoU thresholds

### Interpretation

This is close to standard object detection evaluation.

It evaluates whether predicted boxes match ground-truth boxes under localization criteria.

---

## 10.3 LUNA16

### Task

Lung nodule detection in CT.

### Metric

- FROC
- average sensitivity at predefined false positives per scan

### Predefined FP/scan levels

- 1/8
- 1/4
- 1/2
- 1
- 2
- 4
- 8

### Interpretation

The final score averages sensitivity at these false-positive levels.

---

## 10.4 CAMELYON16

### Task

Metastasis detection in whole-slide images.

### Metric

- FROC
- sensitivity versus average false positives per image

### Interpretation

This evaluates lesion-level detection while accounting for false-positive findings per image.

---

## 10.5 DeepLesion

### Task

Universal lesion detection in CT.

### Metric

- sensitivity at fixed false positives per image

### Example

The paper reports sensitivity at 5 false positives per image.

